# 🎯 Chapter Objective

Is chapter me hum Advanced Link Building aur Backlinks ko detail me samjhenge. Aap seekhenge ki Google backlinks ko kaise evaluate karta hai, high-quality backlinks kaise build kiye jate hain, anchor text kya hota hai, toxic backlinks kya hote hain aur long-term authority build karne ke liye kaunsi strategies use ki jati hain.

---

# 13.1 What is a Backlink?

Backlink ek hyperlink hota hai jo kisi dusri website se aapki website ki taraf point karta hai.

Simple Words:

> **Backlink = Internet par kisi dusri website ka recommendation.**

Example:

```text
Industry Blog

↓

Links to

↓

SafePro Fire Services
```

Google backlinks ko trust signal ke roop me dekhta hai.

---

# 13.2 Why Backlinks are Important?

Backlinks Google ko signal dete hain ki website useful aur trustworthy hai.

Benefits:

* Better Rankings
* Higher Authority
* Faster Indexing
* Referral Traffic
* Better Brand Visibility

---

# 13.3 How Google Evaluates Backlinks?

Google sirf backlinks ki quantity nahi dekhta.

Google evaluate karta hai:

* Website Authority
* Relevance
* Link Placement
* Anchor Text
* Naturalness
* Spam Score

100 spam backlinks se better hai 5 high-quality backlinks.

