# 13.7 Anchor Text

Anchor Text clickable text hota hai.

Good Example:

```text
Fire Extinguisher Installation Services
```

Bad Example:

```text
Click Here
```

Anchor Types:

* Exact Match
* Partial Match
* Branded
* Naked URL
* Generic

Anchor text natural hona chahiye.

